Peter Jessop https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Peter_Jessop 0 Peter Jessop (born June 29, 1964) is an American film actor and voice actor who is known for his video game voice acting. He is known for the voice of Miraak, the primary antagonist of The Elder Scrolls V: Skyrim – Dragonborn DLC, as well as the voice of Paladin Danse from the video game Fallout 4.
